00:38:31,990 --> 00:38:33,140
Moreover,


458
00:38:34,590 --> 00:38:36,070
Tang Siqi is already dead.


459
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:43,460
I killed her.


460
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:46,270
